# Armory - Monitoring Software


Develop a monitoring tool mult-plataform with checks using agents passive/ative and agentless checks using SNMP with a good web interface with easy administration, using cool
technologies.


Below the features planned:
– Passive Monitoring
– Active Monitoring
– Remote commands ( secure remote commands with ssh )
– Simple configuration
– Custom Check
– Perfomance
– Plugins System ( Monitor Apps – Oracle, etc )
– Syslog integration
- Dashboard using Grafana

agent.py and server.py working

Requirements
Cherrypy
Requests
Mongodb
Psutils